			<a href="register.html"><img src="img/pricint_btn_small.png" class="plan_button_style" alt=""></a>
		</div>
		<div class="span4 plan_style2">
			<p class="no_user_style2">SINGLE USER</p>
			<p class="text_style4 text_style_big">99/month, per user</p>
			<p class="text_style5 text_style_big">Store Unlimited</p>
			<p class="text_style6 text_style_big">Candidates</p>
			<a href="register.html"><img src="img/pricint_btn_big.png" class="plan_button_style" alt=""></a>
		</div>
		<div class="span4 plan_style1" id="five_users">
			<p class="no_user_style1">5 + USERS</p>
			<p class="text_style1 text_style">$89/month, per user</p>
			<p class="text_style2 text_style">Store Unlimited</p>
			<p class="text_style3 text_style">Candidates</p>
			<a href="register.html"><img src="img/pricint_btn_small.png" class="plan_button_style" alt=""></a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p id="everything_text">
	Everything in your HootRecruit account is safe, secure and password protected
	</p>
	<div id="faq">
		<p id="faq_head">The Answer Is YES!</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I import candidates from Outlook, Excel, LinkedIn?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I access this on a PC? A Mac? An iPad? An iPhone? An Android Phone?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I cancel anytime?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I find candidates with very specific keywords?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I search for keywords within resumes?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I enter and save notes in my candidates profiles?</p>
		<p class="faq_text">Can I mass email all my candidates from a search result?</p>
